  <brief_title>Eagle AF (Atrial Fibrillation) - Endoscopically Guided Laser Ablation of Persistent Atrial Fibrillation</brief_title>
  <official_title>Eagle AF - Endoscopically Guided Laser Ablation of Persistent Atrial Fibrillation</official_title>
